query:
UPDATE sqs_trigger 
            SET 
                queue_url = $1,
                aws_resource_path = $2,
                message_attributes = $3,
                aws_auth_resource_type = $4,
                script_path = $5,
                path = $6,
                is_flow = $7,
                edited_by = $8,
                email = $9,
                edited_at = now(),
                server_id = NULL,
                error = NULL,
                error_handler_path = $12,
                error_handler_args = $13,
                retry = $14,
                active_mode = $15
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $10 AND path = $11
